OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAmber Heard settles        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdefamation case against    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FDepp                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, US actress Amber Heard will pay Johnny 
OL,6, Depp $1m (#820,000) in a settlement of 
OL,7, their defamation suit, lawyers for Mr  
OL,8, Depp told the BBC.                     
OL,10,FThe former couple faced off in court   
OL,11,Fthis spring in a high-profile battle.  
OL,13,FIn June, a Virginia jury mostly sided  
OL,14,Fwith Mr Depp, 59, finding that Ms Heard
OL,15,Fhad defamed him in an article in which 
OL,16,Fshe called herself a victim of abuse.  
OL,18,FAnnouncing the settlement earlier on   
OL,19,FMonday, Ms Heard, 36, said the decision
OL,20,Fwas "not an act of concession".        
